Package: starsExtra
Title: Miscellaneous functions for working with stars rasters
Version: 0.0.3
Authors@R: 
    person("Michael", "Dorman", email = "dorman@post.bgu.ac.il", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Miscellaneous functions for working with 'stars' objects, mainly single-band rasters. Currently includes functions for: (1) focal filtering, (2) detrending of Digital Elevation Models, and (3) calculating flow length.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.5.0),
    sf,
    stars
Imports:
    methods,
    parallel,
    mgcv
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.1.0
Suggests: 
    testthat (>= 2.1.0)
